\f0\i0\b0 .  It is spoken in the easternmost areas of the Saskan Lands north of the Setta, in the provinces of Pavanarune, Kahilakol, Mobalbesq, and Byenung.  Not so much in Eibar Province, though it is more common to encounter sints there than in other Eibar-speaking provinces. 
