\f2\i Setta
\f0\i0  centric belief and faith systems and ritual.  A liturgical 
\f2\i Sogomsh
\f0\i0  developed in Settarun, where it is preserved, developed and taught especially within the cultural and religious meetings centered in the town of Barbol. 
